<p>Christopher Breen, happily unemployed, joins John and Dave today to do his darndest to help your two favorite geeks solve the world&#39;s problems (by way of answering your Mac and iOS-related questions). Yes, they get geeky, and they also reminisce in the way that only these three long-time geeks (and long-time friends) can. Definitely one you won&#39;t want to miss.</p>
